as we forgive those
who trespass...

22:45.633 --> 22:46.767
So I surrender.

22:46.801 --> 22:49.136
Lead us not into temptation,
but deliver us from evil.

22:49.170 --> 22:50.938
All I know is
I just can't quit on her.

22:50.972 --> 22:52.539
...thine is the Kingdom.

22:52.572 --> 22:53.975
She's the light of my eyes.

22:54.008 --> 22:54.809
...and the glory.

22:54.842 --> 22:56.744
God, please, why her?

22:56.777 --> 22:57.845
Give us this day
our daily bread. And...

22:57.878 --> 22:58.913
I can't understand.

22:58.946 --> 23:01.248
Please, I beg you,
please, please,

23:01.282 --> 23:02.984
bring her back.

23:03.017 --> 23:04.517
Forgive us our trespasses
as we forgive those

23:04.551 --> 23:05.720
who trespass against us.

23:05.753 --> 23:06.787
Forever and ever.

23:08.723 --> 23:09.657
Amen.

23:13.260 --> 23:14.729
Mrs. Watson.

23:18.132 --> 23:21.568
I'm... I'm Christian Baker
from <i>The Chronicle</i>.

23:21.602 --> 23:22.803
Mr. Baker, I'm sorry,

23:22.837 --> 23:25.139
but this is not a good time
for us to talk.

23:25.172 --> 23:27.008
My family is under
a lot of pressure right now.

23:27.041 --> 23:28.009
I just can't...

23:28.042 --> 23:29.777
Well, hey, it's just gonna take
a few minutes.

23:29.810 --> 23:32.146
I'm reporting on how the police
are handling your case.

23:33.214 --> 23:35.082
Nobody is helping us.

23:35.116 --> 23:37.184
Nobody knows anything.

23:37.218 --> 23:39.620
The cops came around,
they searched the building,

23:39.653 --> 23:41.055
and then they just
stopped coming.

23:41.088 --> 23:43.290
The newspapers just ask
the same questions.

23:43.324 --> 23:44.591
I understand.

23:44.625 --> 23:45.893
I might be able to help.

23:46.694 --> 23:48.162
I have a couple of things
that are just...

23:48.195 --> 23:49.330
I needed to talk to you about.

23:49.363 --> 23:50.664
It won't take long.

23:50.698 --> 23:52.066
But I can't do it out here.

23:57.638 --> 23:58.706
It's okay?

24:02.910 --> 24:04.812
You can uh, you can sit here.

24:08.816 --> 24:10.851
Now, we don't have any
hard evidence,

24:10.885 --> 24:13.788
but I... I found a lead
on a suspect

24:13.821 --> 24:16.290
that the cops don't know about.

24:16.323 --> 24:19.193
And my newspaper is gonna
publish an article about it

24:19.226 --> 24:21.128
tomorrow morning
and I thought that

24:21.162 --> 24:23.831
your family should know
before it goes out.

24:23.864 --> 24:26.333
Please do not play with
me, Mr. Baker.

24:26.367 --> 24:29.036
Okay, the last thing we need
is false hope.

24:29.070 --> 24:30.204
No, ma'am.

24:30.237 --> 24:32.039
Now, what I can promise you

24:32.073 --> 24:33.641
is that
when the article comes out,

24:33.674 --> 24:37.778
when people take notice,
the police will be forced

24:37.812 --> 24:39.947
to reinvigorate their search.

25:11.078 --> 25:12.246
Hey, Tiff.

25:13.414 --> 25:15.249
I'm home.

25:15.282 --> 25:18.385
Baby,
I'm in here and we have a guest.

25:18.419 --> 25:20.087
Baby, this is Mr. Baker, he...

25:20.121 --> 25:21.989
What the fuck
are you doing in my house?

25:22.823 --> 25:25.059
- Get the fuck out right now!
- Michael!

25:25.092 --> 25:26.393
I know who he is.

25:26.427 --> 25:28.829
I told you to stay away
from my family.

25:28.863 --> 25:29.630
I understand
you're going through...

25:29.663 --> 25:30.865
You don't understand shit.

25:30.898 --> 25:32.233
Michael, this man can help us.

25:32.266 --> 25:35.236
Nobody is helping us, Tiffany.

25:35.269 --> 25:37.438
Now, I don't know why he's here,
but it's not to help.

25:37.471 --> 25:39.874
You tryin' to write a nice piece
about a poor black family

25:39.907 --> 25:41.675
for all the people downtown
to read over

25:41.709 --> 25:43.010
their morning coffee?

25:43.043 --> 25:44.678
Is that what this is?

25:44.712 --> 25:47.181
Man, my daughter is missing

25:47.214 --> 25:48.949
and the police
don't give a damn about it.

25:48.983 --> 25:50.985
Do you care about that?

25:51.018 --> 25:53.921
Does that part of the story
actually interest you, huh?

25:53.954 --> 25:56.690
- I have information.
- Information, huh?

25:56.724 --> 25:57.892
Why don't you take
your information

25:57.925 --> 26:00.761
and get the fuck
out of my apartment?

26:00.794 --> 26:01.962
Baby?

26:01.996 --> 26:03.731
Michael?

26:03.764 --> 26:04.633
Get the fuck out!

26:04.665 --> 26:05.833
Can you please calm down,
Mr. Watson?

26:05.866 --> 26:06.901
- I'm just trying to help.
- Don't tell me to calm down.

26:06.934 --> 26:07.501
I'll calm down when you
get the fuck out of here.

26:07.535 --> 26:09.136
Baby, please!

26:09.170 --> 26:09.703
Please.

26:09.737 --> 26:11.472
What if he can help us?

26:11.505 --> 26:12.673
Please, Michael.

26:19.446 --> 26:20.347
Look.

26:23.951 --> 26:27.688
I need you to understand that
we are in hell.

26:30.424 --> 26:32.026
Do you get
what I'm saying here?

26:33.861 --> 26:35.396
My daughter is missing

26:35.429 --> 26:37.298
and you know
what the police did about it?

26:39.366 --> 26:42.970
They knocked on couple of doors,
walked through the building,

26:43.003 --> 26:44.305
and then they left.

26:44.338 --> 26:46.140
That is the help we got.

26:46.173 --> 26:49.043
I... I... I guess they got
better shit to do, right?

26:51.345 --> 26:53.514
My son, he can't even go
to school anymore,

26:53.547 --> 26:56.317
because he keeps having
panic attacks.

26:56.350 --> 26:58.953
We don't need
any more reporters,

26:58.986 --> 27:01.222
because it's not gonna get me
a single step closer

27:01.255 --> 27:03.290
to holding my little girl
in my arms.

27:10.231 --> 27:12.199
I'm tired, man.

27:14.535 --> 27:16.870
And I'm scared.

27:22.576 --> 27:24.345
She was so brimming.

27:28.282 --> 27:30.884
She was my everything, man.

27:30.918 --> 27:32.886
You ever have everything
and no money

27:32.920 --> 27:36.390
where all you wanna do
is come home to your family

27:36.423 --> 27:39.526
and that was all you needed,
and then all of a sudden

27:39.560 --> 27:41.929
somethin' comes
and rips your heart out?

27:41.962 --> 27:44.064
Do you have any idea
what that's like?

27:44.098 --> 27:45.866
And then you wonder,
you walk the street

27:45.899 --> 27:47.034
and every child you see

27:47.067 --> 27:49.036
and every little
child's voice you hear,

27:49.069 --> 27:51.038
you think just maybe
it might be your little girl?

27:51.071 --> 27:53.340
Do you have any idea
what that's like?

27:53.374 --> 27:54.475
Do you?

27:58.545 --> 28:01.015
So what are you gonna do
about it, huh?

28:01.048 --> 28:02.383
You're right, Mr. Watson.

28:04.051 --> 28:06.287
The police don't give a damn
about your daughter.

28:08.289 --> 28:10.457
But I might be the only person
who can make 'em.

28:19.900 --> 28:21.368
Now... now I'm listenin'.

28:31.278 --> 28:32.880
Hey, Mike.

28:32.913 --> 28:34.915
Today's paper.

29:22.129 --> 29:26.033
Father,
we come to you right now just thanking you

29:26.701 --> 29:28.936
for everything that
you've done for us.

29:35.509 --> 29:38.078
And make sure she is okay.

29:39.346 --> 29:41.014
She is safe.

29:46.621 --> 29:50.457
And she is warm,
and she's happy.

29:50.491 --> 29:51.558
Please.

29:53.560 --> 29:55.896
That's all I ask of You.

29:57.665 --> 30:01.935
We miss her
and we need her back.

30:07.241 --> 30:09.209
In Your name, we pray.

30:11.178 --> 30:12.680
Amen.

31:47.675 --> 31:48.610
Yeah?

31:49.677 --> 31:51.613
Sam, it's fucking early, man.

31:53.648 --> 31:55.082
Found who?

31:57.317 --> 32:00.287
Yeah, no, I'll meet you...
I'll meet you there.

32:00.320 --> 32:02.055
I'm... I'm leaving now.

32:14.669 --> 32:16.537
- Yo.
- Hey, boss.

32:16.570 --> 32:18.105
Have you seen this little girl?

32:19.273 --> 32:20.574
You mind taking a flyer?

32:20.608 --> 32:21.441
No, I gotta run, man.

32:21.475 --> 32:23.410
No, come on, man,
it's my daughter.

32:23.443 --> 32:24.746
Haven't seen
her, I swear to God.

32:24.779 --> 32:25.780
Just... just... come on...

32:25.813 --> 32:27.281
Just in case.

32:28.716 --> 32:30.417
Hey, just take a look, man.

32:30.450 --> 32:32.119
I uh...

32:32.152 --> 32:34.121
Maybe your neighbors know.

32:39.526 --> 32:41.763
My colleague, Christian and I,
wrote the story, Mr. Baker.

32:41.796 --> 32:42.630
We work at <i>The Chronicle</i>.

32:42.664 --> 32:44.231
- Baker?
- Yeah, that's right, Mr. Baker.

32:44.264 --> 32:45.332
Sounds familiar.

32:45.365 --> 32:46.768
Sam Perkins.
We work at <i>The Chronicle</i>.

32:46.801 --> 32:47.602
I really hope
you find her, because this is a...

32:47.635 --> 32:49.236
- I hope...
- ...it's a tragedy.

33:01.248 --> 33:02.617
- Christian!
- Yeah, what's going on?

33:02.650 --> 33:04.284
Hey.

33:04.318 --> 33:05.152
Okay, is he in yet?

33:05.185 --> 33:06.587
No, he's not in yet.

33:08.221 --> 33:10.390
Well, have you heard anything?

33:10.424 --> 33:11.626
That's him.

33:15.562 --> 33:17.331
Get back!

33:17.364 --> 33:18.398
People move back!

33:18.432 --> 33:20.133
Move back!

33:20.167 --> 33:21.603
When did they
bring you in for questioning?

33:21.636 --> 33:22.837
Yeah, where is the girl?

33:22.870 --> 33:23.838
When did they
bring you in for questioning?

33:23.871 --> 33:25.073
Just uh, move back.

33:25.105 --> 33:27.407
When did they
bring you in for questioning?

33:27.441 --> 33:28.575
Do you know where the girl is?

33:28.610 --> 33:30.410
Are there
any charges at this point?

33:31.411 --> 33:32.680
Everyone stand back.

33:32.714 --> 33:33.748
Back off.
Back off.

34:00.942 --> 34:02.710
Go on.

34:02.744 --> 34:04.578
It was just insane.

34:04.612 --> 34:06.380
I couldn't believe
what I was seeing.

34:06.413 --> 34:07.314
Hmm.

34:07.347 --> 34:10.852
This was like people yelling,
screaming.

34:10.885 --> 34:13.721
The car was halfway up
on the sidewalk.

34:16.691 --> 34:19.526
And she's in the hospital
fighting for her life.

34:19.559 --> 34:21.428
It's okay, Marco.

34:21.461 --> 34:24.398
You did good, you did very good.

34:24.431 --> 34:25.700
Thank you for sharing.

34:32.539 --> 34:34.541
Mr. Watson?

34:34.574 --> 34:35.777
No.

34:42.817 --> 34:44.384
Freddy, welcome back.

34:44.418 --> 34:45.720
Thank you.

34:49.456 --> 34:52.259
So what's going on in there?

34:52.292 --> 34:54.294
We're cracking him, Captain.

34:54.327 --> 34:55.963
He's soft, soft as shit.

34:55.997 --> 34:57.031
Now listen,

34:57.065 --> 34:59.667
fucking press called us out
by finding this guy.

34:59.701 --> 35:01.969
They are making it look like
we are not doing our jobs.

35:02.003 --> 35:04.404
So if this is the guy,
let's pin him quick

35:04.438 --> 35:06.908
and let's wrap this thing up.

35:06.941 --> 35:10.945
And if he's not the guy,
you make him the guy, hmm?

35:10.978 --> 35:12.814
I did not do anything.

35:12.847 --> 35:13.981
I'm innocent.

35:14.015 --> 35:15.983
Please, you have to believe me.

35:16.017 --> 35:17.384
Can you picture?

35:18.585 --> 35:20.822
I mean picture yourself,

35:20.855 --> 35:23.390
walking out the front door
of this station.

35:24.524 --> 35:26.694
You think you can go back
to your job?

35:28.295 --> 35:32.033
Nobody out there cares
what you think you did

35:32.066 --> 35:33.567
or didn't do.

35:33.601 --> 35:36.604
All of New York City
is looking at you.

35:37.905 --> 35:40.307
Every single person.

35:40.340 --> 35:43.443
They all know that you took
that poor,

35:43.477 --> 35:48.315
innocent, little girl
and had your way with her.

35:48.348 --> 35:49.984
I... I did not.

35:50.017 --> 35:51.986
I promise,
I did not do anything.

35:52.019 --> 35:54.454
Plead temporary insanity.

35:54.488 --> 35:56.523
Induced by alcohol abuse.

35:56.556 --> 35:58.525
That's not a bad defense.

35:58.558 --> 36:01.028
I don't care. You get somebody.

36:01.062 --> 36:03.931
That is unless you want
a fuck ton of monkey screaming

36:03.965 --> 36:06.934
in that zoo they call
"the hood" out there.

36:08.836 --> 36:10.638
- You understand me?
- And I don't want that.

36:10.671 --> 36:11.806
No, sir.

36:11.839 --> 36:13.473
I have enough headaches.

36:14.341 --> 36:17.879
So get back in there
and break him down.

36:17.912 --> 36:19.781
Get creative.

36:19.814 --> 36:22.415
Improvise motherfucker,
improvise.

36:23.951 --> 36:25.720
I drink a lot, too.

36:25.753 --> 36:28.089
And the fucked-up part about is
sometimes my memory gets

36:28.122 --> 36:30.423
a little foggy, you know?

36:30.457 --> 36:32.026
Your memory every get foggy?

36:32.059 --> 36:33.426
I... I don't know.

36:33.460 --> 36:35.062
- You ever black out?
- No.

36:35.096 --> 36:36.831
You don't think maybe you...
you blacked out

36:36.864 --> 36:39.934
and you maybe did something
you wouldn't normally do.

36:39.967 --> 36:42.369
Something involving
a little girl?

36:42.402 --> 36:43.805
Please, this is not right
what is happening.

36:43.838 --> 36:45.405
This is not right.

36:54.849 --> 36:56.516
And which day was that?

36:56.550 --> 36:58.552
Forgotten to mention it before.

37:00.087 --> 37:01.789
See, see, see...

37:01.823 --> 37:03.925
I've seen the girl before,
but I did not know her.

37:03.958 --> 37:05.026
You have seen the girl?

37:05.059 --> 37:06.194
Yes.

37:06.227 --> 37:08.595
Before you were saying that
you didn't know anything,

37:09.864 --> 37:10.698
but you have been watching her.

37:10.731 --> 37:12.967
No, no, no, no.
Not at all, not at all.

37:13.000 --> 37:17.504
See, I park my car
in the same spot every morning.

37:17.537 --> 37:19.807
And you watch Monique Watson
walk by!

37:19.841 --> 37:20.975
No, I don't watch her.

37:21.008 --> 37:22.509
I see her walk to school
sometimes.

37:22.542 --> 37:23.376
That's it.

37:23.410 --> 37:24.477
- I don't watch her...
- Nah, ah, ah.

37:24.511 --> 37:25.313
I'll... I'll tell you...
I'll tell you what you did.

37:25.345 --> 37:26.546
I know exactly
how this went down.

37:26.580 --> 37:27.648
No.

37:27.682 --> 37:30.885
You watched that little girl
every day for a month.

37:30.918 --> 37:33.120
- You learned her routine.
- No.

37:33.154 --> 37:35.488
You couldn't wait for
her to walk by in the morning.

37:35.522 --> 37:37.024
And then the day
finally arrived,

37:37.058 --> 37:39.994
you got your phony alibi
all squared away.

37:40.027 --> 37:43.597
And you waited for her
to show up, you fucking monster!

37:43.631 --> 37:45.132
You told her you have something
to show her.

37:45.166 --> 37:46.968
Like we all know
she's a little girl

37:47.001 --> 37:48.468
and you seem like
a nice enough guy.

37:48.501 --> 37:50.171
So why wouldn't she follow you?

37:50.204 --> 37:52.106
- Where did you take her?
- I did not touch her.

37:52.139 --> 37:53.908
I did not touch her,
I did not.

37:53.941 --> 37:55.910
I did not do anything,
I promise.

37:55.943 --> 37:59.412
I did not do anything,
I promise, I promise.

37:59.446 --> 38:01.148
- I promise.
- Are you fucking crying?

38:01.182 --> 38:02.917
No, no.

38:02.950 --> 38:05.485
Are you fucking crying?

38:05.518 --> 38:07.722
I have seen the girl before,
but I did not know.

38:07.755 --> 38:09.422
Yeah,
no shit you've seen the girl,

38:09.456 --> 38:10.958
you sick piece of shit.

38:10.992 --> 38:12.894
How did it feel to grab her...

38:12.927 --> 38:14.461
take her way? Huh?

38:14.494 --> 38:16.764
Did it feel like you were doing
the right thing?

38:16.797 --> 38:17.732
I did not do...

38:17.765 --> 38:19.934
I hope you like getting fucked
in the ass,

38:19.967 --> 38:21.636
because that's exactly
what's gonna happen

38:21.669 --> 38:24.471
when your skinny ass
gets locked up.

38:24.504 --> 38:27.174
We have you on record saying
you were following her.

38:27.208 --> 38:29.176
Might as well tell us the rest!

38:31.078 --> 38:34.782
And maybe...
maybe we can cut you a deal.

38:34.815 --> 38:36.150
Hmm?

38:36.183 --> 38:37.618
What do you say?

38:37.652 --> 38:38.686
I... I never said that.

38:38.719 --> 38:40.021
I never said that,
I didn't.

38:40.054 --> 38:42.156
Are you calling me a liar, huh?

38:42.189 --> 38:43.090
Say it again!

38:43.124 --> 38:44.959
Call me a liar, huh?

38:44.992 --> 38:46.127
- You say it again, huh!
- Cannot breathe.

38:46.160 --> 38:47.560
Hey, hey.
Easy, easy!

38:47.594 --> 38:48.996
- Cannot breathe.
- You ain't nothing.

38:49.030 --> 38:49.964
- Easy!
- You ain't nothing!

38:49.997 --> 38:50.998
- Take it easy.
- You hear me?

38:51.032 --> 38:52.233
You are no-fucking body.

38:52.266 --> 38:55.636
Nobody!

39:26.300 --> 39:29.236
Sir, I finally got a hold
of the rehab center.

39:29.270 --> 39:31.038
Guy's alibi checks out.

39:31.072 --> 39:32.673
Shit, give me that.

39:35.542 --> 39:40.047
His checking date is the day
before the girl disappeared.

39:40.081 --> 39:41.581
You sure this is legit?

39:41.615 --> 39:42.582
The receptionist sent it

39:42.616 --> 39:43.985
and in fact Dr. Bolt confirmed
he was there.

39:44.018 --> 39:45.953
You gotta be fucking kidding me.

40:03.771 --> 40:05.039
Fuck!

40:21.922 --> 40:23.991
<i>He had
likely already passed away</i>

40:24.025 --> 40:26.593
<i>before he was removed
from the police station.</i>

40:26.627 --> 40:27.862
<i>And now
we go to a press release</i>

40:27.895 --> 40:30.731
<i>at the rehabilitation center
that Yann Abelard was attending</i>

40:30.765 --> 40:33.034
<i>days prior to his apprehension
by the police.</i>

40:33.067 --> 40:35.803
<i>I would personally
like to offer my deepest condolences</i>

40:35.836 --> 40:37.772
<i>to Mr. Abelard's family.</i>

40:37.805 --> 40:39.974
<i>In the little experience
I had with him,</i>

40:40.007 --> 40:42.109
<i>he struck me as a good man.</i>

40:42.143 --> 40:45.246
<i>We have no further statement
at this time.</i>

40:50.785 --> 40:52.720
I fucked this up.

40:52.753 --> 40:54.321
You gotta let me make it right.

40:54.355 --> 40:57.258
We fucked this up
and we can't make it right.

40:57.291 --> 40:59.260
We just have to ride it out.

41:00.728 --> 41:02.163
Go home.

41:02.196 --> 41:03.931
Lay low for a while.

41:03.964 --> 41:05.766
If this blows over,

41:05.800 --> 41:07.301
I'll put you back
as soon as I can.

41:07.334 --> 41:08.936
If this blows over?

41:11.238 --> 41:12.572
If it blows over.

42:16.203 --> 42:16.837
You know what I'm saying?

42:16.871 --> 42:18.272
Like he's really interested.

42:18.305 --> 42:19.206
Jesus, man.

42:20.808 --> 42:22.143
Yo.

42:22.176 --> 42:23.878
- Did you...
- Come on, bro.

43:24.205 --> 43:25.372
Who is it?

43:28.075 --> 43:30.411
Mrs. Watson?

43:30.444 --> 43:32.079
It's Christian Baker.

43:33.781 --> 43:35.316
I need to talk to you.

43:39.920 --> 43:42.089
I can't, Mr. Baker.

43:42.122 --> 43:44.091
Please leave before my husband
comes home.

43:44.124 --> 43:45.793
