1:23:16.698 --> 1:23:19.299
Alright everybody,
nothing to see here.

1:23:34.949 --> 1:23:36.851
<i>Now we have
a breaking story in the case</i>

1:23:36.884 --> 1:23:38.720
<i>of a missing local girl.</i>

1:23:38.753 --> 1:23:41.856
<i>Monique Watson disappeared
from her home three weeks ago</i>

1:23:41.889 --> 1:23:44.324
<i>and today the police have
announced a new suspect</i>

1:23:44.358 --> 1:23:46.159
<i>in the unsolved case.</i>

1:23:46.193 --> 1:23:49.831
<i>The family's neighbor,
16-year-old, Marcus Mitchell.</i>

1:23:50.732 --> 1:23:52.366
<i>The police have been
under scrutiny</i>

1:23:52.399 --> 1:23:54.334
<i>since the suicide
of Yann Abelard,</i>

1:23:54.368 --> 1:23:55.903
<i>a taxi driver
who's been questioned</i>

1:23:55.937 --> 1:23:59.473
<i>about the case and took his life
while under custody.</i>

1:23:59.506 --> 1:24:01.274
<i>Marcus Mitchell
attends high school</i>

1:24:01.308 --> 1:24:03.678
<i>with Monique Watson's brother
and his family lives</i>

1:24:03.711 --> 1:24:06.914
<i>in the apartment next door
to the Watson family.</i>

1:24:06.948 --> 1:24:09.416
<i>Police continues to search
for Monique Watson</i>

1:24:09.449 --> 1:24:11.686
<i>and have asked
for the public's support.</i>

1:24:11.719 --> 1:24:13.487
<i>If you have any information
regarding</i>

1:24:13.520 --> 1:24:15.188
<i>Monique Watson's disappearance</i>

1:24:15.222 --> 1:24:18.525
<i>who's been reported missing
on April 2nd...</i>

1:24:32.740 --> 1:24:34.541
You ready to
tell us what happened?

1:24:42.817 --> 1:24:44.551
I skipped school.

1:24:47.254 --> 1:24:51.659
I went to the Watsons' house,
I knocked on the door.

1:25:01.368 --> 1:25:02.837
Monique answered.

1:25:04.972 --> 1:25:06.774
I asked if anybody else is home.

1:25:09.711 --> 1:25:10.778
She said nah.

1:25:13.047 --> 1:25:14.949
Told her my mom needed
to talk to her.

1:25:18.686 --> 1:25:19.887
I took her to my bedroom.

1:25:21.055 --> 1:25:22.924
Told her to take
all her clothes off.

1:25:23.958 --> 1:25:26.393
But she didn't want to, though.

1:25:26.426 --> 1:25:28.495
I could tell
she was really scared.

1:25:29.296 --> 1:25:31.364
She kept promising
not to tell anybody

1:25:31.398 --> 1:25:32.734
if I just let her go.

1:25:33.801 --> 1:25:35.268
I didn't believe that shit
though.

1:25:36.104 --> 1:25:40.540
And I picked her up,
and I put her on my bed,

1:25:42.043 --> 1:25:43.811
and she barely even fought.

1:25:44.979 --> 1:25:47.782
Then my brain started working
real fast,

1:25:47.815 --> 1:25:49.016
I thought,
"Ain't no way she'd be able

1:25:49.050 --> 1:25:50.517
to keep that a secret."

1:25:50.550 --> 1:25:53.453
It was as if somebody else
was doing it.

1:25:53.487 --> 1:25:55.857
Like I was just standing there
watching it happen.

1:25:57.324 --> 1:25:58.291
And I hit her.

1:26:00.494 --> 1:26:01.696
Real hard.

1:26:01.729 --> 1:26:03.363
Boom!

1:26:09.503 --> 1:26:11.271
And I was watching
Tyrell's crib.

1:26:12.640 --> 1:26:14.474
He's my neighbor
and a good buddy of mine.

1:26:15.610 --> 1:26:16.576
He left me his keys,

1:26:16.611 --> 1:26:19.847
so it was easy to put
her inside his apartment

1:26:19.881 --> 1:26:22.817
and after into the storage
next to the body

1:26:22.850 --> 1:26:24.417
of the other girl.

1:26:25.519 --> 1:26:27.420
Nobody knew a thing.

1:26:28.923 --> 1:26:29.957
Every day I wanted to end her,

1:26:29.991 --> 1:26:35.763
but seeing the body
of the other girl, I just...

1:26:35.797 --> 1:26:37.330
I wasn't ready to do it again.

1:26:38.800 --> 1:26:40.768
Just fuck that shit.

1:26:40.802 --> 1:26:42.569
It was funny though.

1:26:42.603 --> 1:26:44.672
I was giving her food and water.

1:26:45.505 --> 1:26:48.475
Took good care of her
like she was my daughter,

1:26:48.508 --> 1:26:49.476
you know?

1:26:50.945 --> 1:26:52.914
I even forgot about the one
in the box.

1:26:58.052 --> 1:27:01.088
Mhmm, the end.

1:27:26.013 --> 1:27:28.049
- Hey.
- Morning, detective.

1:27:28.082 --> 1:27:29.349
What we got here.

1:27:40.862 --> 1:27:44.866
Hello, um,
my name is Michael Watson.

1:27:45.900 --> 1:27:47.001
It's been seven days

1:27:47.034 --> 1:27:49.502
since my daughter Monique
was found.

1:27:50.403 --> 1:27:53.808
It's been the hardest ride
of my life,

1:27:53.841 --> 1:27:55.575
it was like I died,
and went to hell,

1:27:55.610 --> 1:27:57.111
and came back a week ago.

1:27:59.180 --> 1:28:00.715
Every day we spent without her

1:28:00.748 --> 1:28:03.150
made me fall deeper
and deeper into a hole.

1:28:03.184 --> 1:28:08.588
This really dark, cold,
scary pit.

1:28:09.589 --> 1:28:11.491
And I'm embarrassed to say this,

1:28:12.559 --> 1:28:13.995
but I thought
about killing myself

1:28:14.028 --> 1:28:15.897
more than a few times.

1:28:16.898 --> 1:28:21.568
I couldn't see past
any of the madness, you know?

1:28:21.602 --> 1:28:25.172
Even now with my baby girl home,
I still have these...

1:28:26.707 --> 1:28:29.576
these mind trips,
these panic attacks

1:28:29.610 --> 1:28:31.478
when she's not near me,
you know?

1:28:31.511 --> 1:28:35.216
And I wonder if...
if it all really happened

1:28:35.249 --> 1:28:38.052
or if it's just a really,
really bad dream.

1:28:39.020 --> 1:28:42.555
But something, something
inside me kept me going,

1:28:42.589 --> 1:28:43.423
you know?

1:28:44.491 --> 1:28:46.661
My wife says it was God's grace.

1:28:47.929 --> 1:28:48.763
Had to be.

1:28:48.796 --> 1:28:50.898
I, by myself,
I wasn't strong enough.

1:28:52.667 --> 1:28:57.972
When my daughter was safe,
and we were together,

1:28:58.005 --> 1:29:01.976
and I can find her, and breathe.

1:29:04.078 --> 1:29:07.782
I needed to come here tonight
to say thank you

1:29:07.815 --> 1:29:10.483
to each and every one of you
for being here for me.

1:29:11.484 --> 1:29:16.624
You all will always be my rock
and I hope I can be yours, too.

1:29:17.391 --> 1:29:20.861
It's a promise I've made to God
and I'm damn sure will keep it.

1:29:22.997 --> 1:29:24.966
My name is Michael Watson.

1:29:26.734 --> 1:29:28.468
And I have two children.

1:29:29.603 --> 1:29:31.538
My daughter went missing
six weeks ago

1:29:31.571 --> 1:29:33.040
and now she's found.

1:29:35.609 --> 1:29:40.014
And God is good, all the time.

